<paragraph id="4B5B2900DB6AC47C09E3F932CE3AF8B7" blockId="2.[166,1225,1670,1857]" pageId="2" pageNumber="97">
Distribution. Widespread in Europe (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6AC47C0BEDF932CCDBF917" author="Nentwig, W. &amp; Blick, T. &amp; Gloor, D. &amp; Hanggi, A. &amp; Kropf, C." box="[725,988,1670,1697]" pageId="2" pageNumber="97" refId="ref9667" refString="Nentwig, W., Blick, T., Gloor, D., Hanggi, A., Kropf, C. 2021. Araneae. Version 02.2021. https: // www. araneae. nmbe. ch (accessed 13.02.2021)" type="url" year="2021">Nentwig et al., 2021</bibRefCitation>
). 
<collectingCountry id="33F36990DB6AC47C0ACFF932CB5DF916" box="[1015,1114,1670,1696]" name="Ukraine" pageId="2" pageNumber="97">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
: Kyivske Polissia (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6AC47C0829F912CEEDF977" author="Evtushenko, K. V." box="[273,490,1702,1729]" pageId="2" pageNumber="97" pagination="91" refId="ref8612" refString="Evtushenko, K. V. 1991. Ecological and faunistic studies of spiders (Aranei) in Kievskoye Polessie. Editorial board of ' Vestnik Zoologii'. Deposit in VINITI 04.06. 91. N 2338 - V 91." type="book chapter" year="1991">Evtushenko, 1991</bibRefCitation>
), 
<collectingRegion id="8920E7E2DB6AC47C0B39F912CD67F976" box="[513,608,1702,1728]" country="Ukraine" name="Kharkiv" pageId="2" pageNumber="97">Kharkiv</collectingRegion>
Reg. (first record). Further to the east occurs from West Siberia (Kemerovo) (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6AC47C08DFF972CDC2F957" author="Trilikauskas, L. A." box="[487,709,1734,1761]" pageId="2" pageNumber="97" pagination="438 - 450" refId="ref11868" refString="Trilikauskas, L. A. 2013. On the fauna of spiders and harvestmen (Arachnida: Aranei et Opiliones) of Gornaya Shoria, South Siberia. Eurasian Entomological Journal, 12, 438 - 450 [In Russian with English summary]." type="journal article" year="2013">Trilikauskas, 2013</bibRefCitation>
) to the Russian Far East (
<bibRefCitation id="2F7554F1DB6AC47C0AC6F972CBC2F956" author="Mikhailov, K. G." box="[1022,1221,1734,1760]" pageId="2" pageNumber="97" pagination="1 - 260" refId="ref9538" refString="Mikhailov, K. G. 2013. The spiders (Arachnida: Aranei) of Russia and adjacent countries: a non-annotated checklist. Arthropoda Selecta, Supplement 3, 1 - 260." type="journal article" year="2013">Mikhailov, 2013</bibRefCitation>
; WOS, 2021).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4B5B2900DB6AC47C09E3F8B3CD9DF8F6" blockId="2.[166,1225,1670,1857]" pageId="2" pageNumber="97">
